name: Jetrabbit Valley
description:
... can the rabbit reach the moon?

Manage your jetpack's fuel as you plant, grow, and harvest vegetables along the steep walls of a valley. Profits from your crops will upgrade your jetpack's fuel capacity-- letting you fly higher and higher to farm more of the walls.

---

Made in one weekend for Astrojone's Lost Cartridge Jam 2.

  • Music by ravancloak
  • Sound effects: Retro SFX Asset Pack
